title: Mv多世界插件无法识别AskyBlock空岛插件的空岛世界
author: Back_Wheel
txt_content: 今天开了个空岛服用的是AskyBlock插件，然后我输入/mv list的时候空岛世界（AskyBlock）显示为unloaded,然后我尝试用/mv load AskyBlock加载空岛世界也没有用，请问这个问题怎么解决？（不是什么无常驻内存的问题，因为我设置空岛世界为主世界），我之所以要加载这个世界是为了禁止动物的自然生成，如果有其他方法解决也可以。

replies.author: schorsch
replies.txt_content:
要不试试GitHub上的
https://github.com/tastybento/as ... k-is-the-main-world


How do I set up my server so that ASkyBlock is the main world?
Start with a new server install (recommended)

Run the server like normal to set it up - it will created default worlds, i.e., world, world_nether, world_the_end

Stop the server

Copy in plugins that you need, e.g., Essentials, WorldEdit, PermissionsEx, and Vault 1.5.

Copy in ASkyBlock.jar to plugins folder

Edit server.properties to list ASkyBlock as the world, i.e., 'level-name=ASkyBlock'

Edit bukkit.yml to have this at the end (the spaces are VERY important to get right):

worlds:
  ASkyBlock:
    generator: ASkyBlock
If you are running the new nether, then you should also add:

worlds:
  ASkyBlock:
    generator: ASkyBlock
  ASkyBlock_nether:
    generator: ASkyBlock
If you change the name of the world, then change the world name, but NOT the generator name. For example:

worlds:
  SkyBlockWorld:
    generator: ASkyBlock
  SkyBlockWorld_nether:
    generator: ASkyBlock

多世界要不试试新版本的。。。

the console says that plugin cannot start because it cannot register the generator with Multiverse
You see an error in the console that says the ASkyBlock generator could not be registered. This is usually caused by Multiverse. Make sure you are using the latest version of the Multiverse plugin. Older versions do not allow the generator to be set. You will see an error saying that.

If that does not work, make sure you are actually shutting down your server and restarting instead of using reload. That will ensure ASkyBlock’s generator is loaded and ready.
